{%- style -%}
  .terms-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 60px auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #333;
  }

  .terms-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .terms-header h1 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: #000;
  }

  .terms-section {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .terms-section h2 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    color: #000;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .terms-section p {
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .terms-section ul {
    padding-left: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .terms-section li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .terms-footer {
    margin-top: 60px;
    padding-top: 30px;
    border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #666;
    text-align: center;
  }
{%- endstyle -%}

<div class="terms-container">
  <div class="terms-header">
    <h1>Terms & Conditions</h1>
    <p>Last Updated: {{ 'now' | date: "%B %d, %Y" }}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="terms-section">
    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>Welcome to Lishra. By accessing and using our website and purchasing <strong>Lishra Beauty Cream</strong>, you agree to comply with and be bound by the following terms and conditions. Please read them carefully.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="terms-section">
    <h2>2. Product Use & Safety</h2>
    <p>Our beauty products are designed for external use only. To ensure the best results and safety:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Always perform a patch test on a small area of skin 24 hours before full application.</li>
      <li>Discontinue use immediately if irritation or redness occurs.</li>
      <li>Keep products out of reach of children and direct sunlight.</li>
      <li>Lishra is not responsible for any adverse reactions due to improper use or unknown skin sensitivities.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="terms-section">
    <h2>3. Shipping & Delivery</h2>
    <p>We strive to deliver your orders as quickly as possible. Typical shipping times are:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Standard Shipping: 3-5 business days within the country.</li>
      <li>Order processing takes 24-48 hours.</li>
      <li>Tracking numbers will be provided once the order has been dispatched.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="terms-section">
    <h2>4. Returns & Refunds</h2>
    <p>Due to the nature of beauty products, we only accept returns for items that are:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Unopened and in their original packaging.</li>
      <li>Returned within 14 days of purchase.</li>
      <li>Damaged upon arrival (photo evidence required).</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="terms-section">
    <h2>5. Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p>All content on this website, including text, graphics, logos, and product names (such as Lishra Beauty Cream), is the property of Lishra and protected by international copyright laws.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="terms-footer">
    <p>If you have any questions regarding these terms, please contact us at support@lishra.store</p>
    <p>&copy; {{ 'now' | date: "%Y" }} Lishra Beauty. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Terms Content",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Terms Content"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
